writing skills, experience with both short- and long-form content - Editing/proofreading pro - Passion for trying out new ways to engage users on social media - A knowledge of financial products/industry, FinTech, or the crypto space Perks of working at BlockFi: - Huge opportunities for professional development as BlockFi expands its product lines and geographies internationally - Work alongside an enthusiastic, collegial, and driven team - Unlimited vacation / sick days - Fully paid health benefits - Weekly lunches and office snacks Skills B2C content experience, short and long-form content experience, social media experience, knowledge of fintech and crypto Compensation 65,000 - 75,000 Applications for this job are currently closed. "
